data.description:
Best Value on the Market! Introducing 11780 Merritt Way in Castroville, CA! This home offers 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a generous 1849 square feet of living space on a 7405 square foot lot.  Priced for a quick AS-IS sell and will requires TLC, making it an excellent opportunity for customization.  Step inside to generous size living room with fireplace opening into the kitchen and dining area space. Home has expanded its footprint to include a comfortable sized separate family room with beamed ceiling. A versatile space for various activities. One Bedroom hosts full bathroom and sliding glass door to the backyard. Original Primary Bedroom has walk in closet and 1/2 bath along with sliding glass door also private access up to backyard.  Property has double paned windows, fruit trees, shed and a spacious fenced backyard, water filtration system has been installed, refrigerator 2023yr, washer, dryer all conveys with sale.  Shopping - restaurants walking distance. Simple access to all Hwy 1, 101 & 156. Monterey - 15 min., Santa Cruz - 25, San Jose -50.  THE BEACH & Moss Landing minutes away! Don't miss the potential of this home. Explore the possibilities!
Square footage, acreage, and other information and has not been verified by Seller or Listing Agent.
